relation: Dungeon Man. Experimenting with watercolour pencils, on printer paper. I wanted to try out my new watercolour pencils, so I started testing them on regular paper, with plans to eventually move on to watercolour paper that wouldn't wrinkle so bad. The paper IS quite wrinkled, but I pressed on my scanner lid pretty hard to flatten the scan out. :D
It's Duster. And he's jumping. Jump Duster, jump.
Good gravy, it's me dressed up and coiffed up as Duster. The pants are a recolour, since, NO, I don't have any pink pants.
